About
This is a HapiJS API. Authorization is already configured by default using JWT and runs on all routes (This can be disabled on specific routes in their options). Functional Testing can easily be implemented an all routes as seen in auth.test.js.

Setup
Copy "example.config.js" to a new file named "config.js".
Configure mongo database for application.
Run "npm start" command.

npm commands:
+npm start - will start node server.
+npm test - will run all tests in "./test/" using lab -v.